creator: Dora Sigerson Shorter
description:
LibriVox recording of The Sad Years by Dora Sigerson Shorter.
Read in English by Jeremiah Sutherland; Lucretia B.; Ken Masters; Carol; Ian King; KHand; AnnaMarie Tokas; Richard Carter
This is a collection of poems by Dora Sigerson Shorter, whose subject are the Sad Years 1914-1918. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
